Package Files

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Editable
    editable interface extends Viewable interface by giving the access to edit file(delete, edit)
    Viewable
    Viewable is used to give user permission to view file
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    CustomJLabel
    CustomJLabel extends JLabel by adding MyFile object, which is used to give information about the icon of the file and other data from MyFile class
    CustomJLabelFolders
    CustomJLabelForders extends JLabel by adding Icon object, which is used to give information about the folder icon and other data from Icon class
    Docum
    Docum extends MyFile and it is used for document(odt,docx) file types
    EditableFile
    EditableFile abstract class implements Editable interface
    FileFactory
    FileFactory class implements method-factory design pattern
    Icon
    Class Icon is used to store information about specific icon
    Image
    Image extends MyFile and it is used for image(jpg,png) file types
    Media
    Media extends MyFile and it is used for Media(mp3,mp4) file types
    MyFile
    Base file Class, it is used to store basic file data: file size, file name, file directory, creation time, modification time, execution program
    SimpleFile
    SimpleFile extends MyFile and it is used as a unknown file type
  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    FileIsMissingException
    FileIsMissingException is used to inform user that specific file, by given name does not exist
    IncorrectFileNameException
    An exception class which extends FileIsMissingException class It is used to inform user that, file name has some symbols in the name that are forbidden in file name: Invalid symbols: $%\\/:*?\"'>|~`#^+={}[];!
